-- Brazil Government Warns of Gasoline Shortage by Year-End: Folha
-- B y   F a b i o l a   M o u r a
-- 2012-11-04T15:09:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-04/brazil-government-warns-of-gasoline-shortage-by-year-end-folha.html
There is a risk of gasoline shortages
in coming months due to increased consumption during the
holidays, Folha de S. Paulo newspaper reported, citing sugar-
cane industry group Unica’s technical director Antonio de Padua
Rodrigues.
* Brazil ’s govt. is meeting with oil-sector cos. in an effort to
avoid problems, oil distributors union Sindicom Pres. Alisio Vaz
said, according to Folha  To contact the reporter on this story:
